data.description: Come check out this 2 bedroom home located in Milan, IL! This home offers a large eat-in kitchen that walks out to the back deck. You will love the updated main floor bathroom. A 3rd bedroom in basement is ready to be finished. Updated exterior paint. Backyard has a deck, shed and partially fenced yard. 30x24 oversized 2-car garage. Call today to schedule an appointment!
